text: Kim and Kanye seen together for the first time since birth of Chicago ( Picture : Splash News ) Proud parents Kim Kardashian and Kanye West have been spotted enjoying a low - key date days after welcoming baby Chicago. On Friday Kanye was spotted alone and offering a rare smiling after the couple announced the birth of their new daughter via surrogate on 16 January. But on Saturday Kim, who has two other children with Kanye, finally joined her hubby for the first time and it looks having a newborn in the house has not really affected their sleep, as neither look like they ’ ve lost a wink of sleep.
